parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Slow DC Charging at Low Temperatures

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The limited charging rate of the vehicle can cause inconvenience and safety concerns, as it may lead to prolonged charging times, potentially stranding drivers and passengers.
